# .claude: commit shareable agent config (skills/commands/workflows/settings),
# ignore machine-local runtime state.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/workflows/
!.claude/settings.json
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
